{"type":"message","id":"c7dde65f","parentId":"17b66d0c","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:07:38.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OpenClaw 每日资讯任务完成\n\n已生成今日（2026-03-27）OpenClaw 资讯文章，保存在：  \n`/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260327.md`\n\n## 本期内容要点\n\n- **最新版本**：v2026.3.24 于 3 月 25 日发布\n- **主要更新**：Gateway OpenAI 兼容性增强、全新技能管理界面、Microsoft Teams 集成升级、Docker 容器支持、多项 UI 优化\n- **修复重点**：安全沙箱绕过问题、网关重启会话恢复、多个渠道消息路由问题\n\n任务状态已更新为 `completed`。\n</parameter></function></seed:tool_call>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1737,"output":184,"cacheRead":22328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24249,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774573649078}}
